<title>SOUTH AFRICA: GFP expects final offers on stake sale soon.</title>
<headline>GFP expects final offers on stake sale soon.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-06-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>South Africa's Gold Fields Property Co Ltd said on Wednesday that it expected final offers for the sale of the stake of one of its principal shareholders in the next few weeks.</p>
<p>&quot;The prcess of disposal...has reached the point where final offers are expected from a number of prospective purchasers within the next few weeks,&quot; the firm said in a statement.</p>
<p>It added that shareholders should exercise caution when trading in its shares.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
